{"tid":1968454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人生好似無乜意義","createTime":"2020-04-11T16:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T17:23:50.000Z","uid":312611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc05f3872f1b84e73bddf3cb5702cbb46108695f","tid":1968454,"uid":312611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"呢個世界好似無咩值得留戀<br />\n<br />\n離開嘅離關 走嘅走 而我仲要係一個只係識呃身邊人嘅垃圾 屋企人 女朋友 朋友都通通俾我呃住<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日嘅沉澱令我明白到 我繼續留低係世上嘅意義好似唔係無想像中咁重要<br />\n<br />\n如果要諗係離開前嘅一刻想做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n我諗會係以一命換一命嘅方式殺警曱 以報手足之仇<br />\n<br />\n淨下嘅路交俾手足繼續行"},{"pid":"fd47b4d43492c7cf810b900a64f743e1627db0c6","tid":1968454,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"我都想死 呢個世界唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fad94f45178091dfe36d6f5fbca86587a43b919","tid":1968454,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d25477bbda2bcf9dee2e78f7fe3811f7f809ac6","tid":1968454,"uid":312611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd47b4d43492c7cf810b900a64f743e1627db0c6","tid":1968454,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"我都想死 呢個世界唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"女又走 屋企人又過身<br />\n人生無乜意義可言"}]}